Package: pubmedclient
Title: PubMed and PMC API Client
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("illumination-k", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "illumination27@gmail.com")
Description: R bindings for the Rust 'pubmed-client' library. Provides access to
    the PubMed and PubMed Central (PMC) APIs for searching, fetching article
    metadata, and retrieving full text or Markdown. Wraps the high-performance
    asynchronous Rust client behind a synchronous R interface.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc
Config/rextendr/version: 0.3.1
URL: https://github.com/illumination-k/pubmed-client
BugReports: https://github.com/illumination-k/pubmed-client/issues
